"The Billionaire Raj."

00:59:10.080 --> 00:59:11.620
I'd highly, highly recommend it.

00:59:11.620 --> 00:59:14.640
I think you do a phenomenal job
in just a series of portraits

00:59:14.640 --> 00:59:17.670
of the billionaire Raj,
kind of this class,

00:59:17.670 --> 00:59:20.160
really getting at a lot
of the thorny issues that

00:59:20.160 --> 00:59:23.100
are central to India's
development over the course

00:59:23.100 --> 00:59:24.890
of the next half century.

00:59:24.890 --> 00:59:26.140
Thanks, James, for being here.

